trends: There have been 3 other sightings in Ulysses
There was one other sighting in Ulysses on or around September 7th 2009
divs: Sighting DetailsIt came out of the south west went almost right above Ulysses but just to the north of it in a north east heading till out of sight.It was the same brightness all the time it didn't turn or get any lower. It was moving faster then most jets but there was no noise.This didn't look like a meteor or a satellite or an aircraft it was bright and looked about the same size as a street light but almost to bright to look at and there wasn't a trail left behind it.
Summary: It came out of the south west when almost right above Ulysses but just to the north of it in a north east heading till out of sight.
